Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.30,0:01:57.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,(所罗门攻略战)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.86,0:02:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第三舰队，从后方接近中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:20.59,0:02:21.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地听到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.90,0:02:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,听到了，请说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.17,0:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,今后准备补给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.97,0:02:28.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,改变航路\N进入同样的队形
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.87,0:02:30.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,进入补给状态
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,告诉他明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.61,0:02:37.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,输送舰波伦布司\N向右前方驶去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.65,0:02:39.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快准备补给
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.65,0:02:41.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我去和司令打招呼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:45.79,0:02:47.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么我不可以去？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.62,0:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也要和司令打招呼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.92,0:02:51.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又不是去玩\N有什么好去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.13,0:02:54.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错了，只是去打招呼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.33,0:02:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,史中尉\N不如帮一帮忙，好吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.13,0:02:59.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,气死人了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.25,0:03:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拿着火箭的\N那怪家伙是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.62,0:03:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是突袭快艇！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.59,0:03:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突袭快艇？\N又不是要去打仗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.76,0:03:25.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,提起也怕怕！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.10,0:03:33.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗，待会再见！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.57,0:03:35.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,舰长，白色基地舰长\N来了等你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.87,0:03:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:39.14,0:03:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我是布莱特中尉，请指教！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,辛苦你了，布莱特！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.94,0:03:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很久不见了，马健司令！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.58,0:03:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要叫我做司令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:48.58,0:03:49.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那些大人物一到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.25,0:03:51.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我就成为小人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.35,0:03:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你现在很有指挥官的气势
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.83,0:03:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真不错呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.46,0:04:01.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,过来看看！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.46,0:04:04.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是我们现在\N行驶中的路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.47,0:04:07.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会将所有军力\N集中过来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.17,0:04:12.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这么说\N目的地是所罗门吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.97,0:04:15.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，白色基地和我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.81,0:04:17.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是去攻击所罗门的\N先锋部队！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.21,0:04:20.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗！任务相当艰巨呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.55,0:04:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们可以做得到吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:22.98,0:04:25.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你能够提出\N这个问题和我说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,足以证明你是有能力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.76,0:04:29.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定不会有问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.29,0:04:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过，母舰上的驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.66,0:04:35.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已经超时工作了！\N特别是阿姆罗...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.80,0:04:37.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,呀！你指那个\N驾驶钢弹的少年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.63,0:04:40.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他算是个天才\N和我们不同的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.00,0:04:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他不同的吗？\N你说不是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.18,0:04:50.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为什么电压\N会装不上去的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.44,0:04:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那便糟了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.91,0:04:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吃饭了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.79,0:05:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么不妥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:00.45,0:05:03.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不...只要放下便可以了\N多谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.46,0:05:05.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可能我太倦了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.91,0:05:23.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们只送一个毕克．萨姆的\N机动堡垒来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.91,0:05:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！只是得一个！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.08,0:05:29.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底多姆在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.15,0:05:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,靠这些多姆的数量\N怎会够...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.55,0:05:34.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,若只得一个新型机的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.12,0:05:36.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,倒不如给我\N十台多姆还好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.16,0:05:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是这样的...      什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.16,0:05:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个毕克．萨姆还是在试作阶段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然已在急速进行...\N但是...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.27,0:05:46.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各方面来的订单\N实在太多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,算数吧！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.84,0:05:52.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快将毕克．萨姆组合好！   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.77,0:05:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,布加，现在还未知\N帝姆舰队在哪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.11,0:05:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真的对不起！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.61,0:05:59.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为现在米诺夫斯基粒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.25,0:06:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,浓度最高的地方作探测\N所以...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.88,0:06:05.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要尽快找到他们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:18.20,0:06:19.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,立刻除去固定轴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.73,0:06:22.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开启输送管\N开启所有通道！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.94,0:06:25.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,打开港外通道\N立刻准备离港！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,麻烦你了，卡姆兰检察官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请问解除封条了吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,已解除了\N但请别胡乱开火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.66,0:06:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有请你们快离开\N以后别再来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:48.90,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我希望你说话客气一些\N卡姆兰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.90,0:06:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.97,0:06:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星六号能够\N平安苟存到今日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.50,0:06:58.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,都是吉翁军手下留情！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.77,0:07:01.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是否还要我多谢你们吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.51,0:07:03.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，你在做什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.98,0:07:39.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,她...她是谁？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.65,0:07:42.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就当是我的妹妹吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:16.12,0:08:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在，我们舰队的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:17.99,0:08:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由所罗门计起来\N应该是第三战区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好像是鼻尖的位置！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.63,0:08:26.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在这里，我们已\N再没任何障碍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,阻碍住去所罗门的路线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.70,0:08:30.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,又来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.23,0:08:34.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请各舰队排成横一字形！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳‧波，小琪她们怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.81,0:08:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们在五号室\N有重力的那间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.91,0:08:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,哈罗也在？         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.15,0:08:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小琪，你知不知\N为何要穿成这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.52,0:08:51.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为不穿成这样\N是不可去打仗的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.92,0:08:56.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,起初由正面攻击\N跟着用雷射光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.16,0:08:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,然后大家由缺口攻入去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.33,0:09:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？你不是说笑吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.20,0:09:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,单就这样的兵力...\N去攻击...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.16,0:09:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,岂不是去自杀吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.50,0:09:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不用担心，凯\N联邦军会想到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.53,0:09:09.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎可叫我可放心呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.50,0:09:11.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你说得太多了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.87,0:09:14.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一定要相信帝姆舰队的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.18,0:09:17.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各位只要维持\N5分钟就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:18.35,0:09:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到那时，本军会用\N攻击要塞武器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:21.45,0:09:24.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,攻击要塞武器？\N是什么武器的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.62,0:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始攻击！速度加八度！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.49,0:09:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,突袭快艇准备！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.36,0:09:33.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,2...1...0...出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.15,0:09:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到底敌军的\N移动情形怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.48,0:09:57.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，他们已集合在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:57.82,0:10:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,向我们接近\N可以使用雷射炮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.62,0:10:01.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！通通击沉他们！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.40,0:10:13.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,火箭炮，主炮\N雷射炮开始攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.50,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发射！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.13,0:10:48.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人发射了雷射扰乱网！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多姆，各MS\N出击应付敌人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.17,0:10:55.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军数目不多\N改用火箭可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,密特舰队向左面伸展过去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,附助机部队在后方别动！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.28,0:11:03.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帝姆主力舰\N会由那边来的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.32,0:11:09.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷射优乱纲成功了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.82,0:11:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！各舰队各自进攻！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.33,0:11:16.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本舰现立即出动！\N吉姆立即出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.10,0:11:26.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,机动战士\NG战机，出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家记着，要共同作战！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.88,0:11:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家别迟到啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.45,0:11:37.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一定会努力作战的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.95,0:11:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，现在出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢加农，出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.36,0:11:47.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,出发！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.65,0:12:14.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个就是...战场？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.18,0:12:44.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶，看我的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.25,0:12:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,下一个呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.46,0:12:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,凯，要小心敌人呀！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.63,0:12:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雪拉，你真可爱呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.97,0:13:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马加，替我指挥一会！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.84,0:13:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，将军！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:05.84,0:13:06.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我很快回来的！      是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.81,0:13:14.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,万全之策\N女仕请全部退避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,到逃生船去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.85,0:13:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,战局对我们不利吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.42,0:13:23.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.56,0:13:26.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门是不会被攻陷的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.83,0:13:27.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这只是为安全计！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.33,0:13:31.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所谓不怕一万，只怕万一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.60,0:13:34.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,况且，也是为了\N小宝贝的安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.10,0:13:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你太大声了，吓坏她呢！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:42.58,0:13:43.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没错，再过一些\N再一些，是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.63,0:14:06.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,生或死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.13,0:14:09.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信只有在战争后才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不过有一点可以肯定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:12.34,0:14:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,当每次闪起美丽的光辉时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.14,0:14:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,就会有数个人甚至数百人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.91,0:14:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,变成太空一粒小尘而消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.27,0:14:41.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射镜准备得怎样？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.84,0:14:43.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是！大约\N四分钟左右便行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.27,0:14:45.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来敌军快将发现我们了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.11,0:14:48.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么？蠢材！现在才发现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.81,0:14:50.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军躲在岩石后面？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.91,0:14:51.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.11,0:14:53.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是帝姆！敌军的主力舰队
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.81,0:14:54.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还不快攻击？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.59,0:15:00.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.83,0:15:11.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派武断号和天力号\N去封付敌主力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.63,0:15:15.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要不要第七团派援军来？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.17,0:15:23.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希莉亚？\N岂非会给国民成笑话？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.88,0:15:33.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射镜装置妥当！\N在主力轴上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.32,0:15:34.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,电能已经连接好！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.59,0:15:35.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射战术开始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.22,0:15:37.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目标是所罗门右翼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.82,0:15:39.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙大门！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.27,0:15:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,反射开始倒数十秒！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.01,0:15:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有敌舰接近，小心！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.91,0:15:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不必理它，快对准重点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.28,0:16:04.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,三...二...焦点...对准！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.64,0:16:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门...烧着了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.74,0:16:29.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军的\N新武器威力很利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.51,0:16:35.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么事？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.75,0:16:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们的宇宙大门破了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.92,0:16:37.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是敌军的新武器！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是什么？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.75,0:16:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,雷达仍可用\N但发电机就失效了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.99,0:16:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,联邦军攻入来了吗？\N位置在那里？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.99,0:16:47.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军主力舰队来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.89,0:16:49.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,主力舰应该\N可以应付到的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:49.96,0:16:52.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,报告\N有数百小飞弹来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.30,0:16:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要向那边攻击才是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.01,0:17:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,糟了...\N连枪弹口也没有了...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.15,0:17:11.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还是先回去吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:14.96,0:17:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,白色基地已归航\N损伤程度B
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人负伤，因为坦克撤退
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.73,0:17:23.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以战斗力下降了11%
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.86,0:17:26.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人和很多人也受了伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.73,0:17:28.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不如由我\N到医疗室帮忙吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.94,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好，保罗\N你代替芙劳‧波的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.07,0:17:33.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是，我来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.48,0:17:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正木上仕\N请你准备输血吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.49,0:17:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很快会康复的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:49.46,0:17:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有什么事我可以帮忙的？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.09,0:17:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,帮我拿AB型血桨\N及输血设备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.10,0:17:57.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人？         快点！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.47,0:18:01.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌军主力舰来了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:02.10,0:18:03.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,用卫星火箭攻击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.10,0:18:05.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,将基地内\N所有导弹发射出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.35,0:18:15.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,最重要的是\N为隼人多输一樽血
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.18,0:18:17.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请记住！         是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.65,0:18:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,即管来吧！   多姆！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.69,0:18:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,芙劳‧波...？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,请你别激动\N已经充份地作战了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.80,0:18:31.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吗？所以要安静啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大家呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.63,0:18:35.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们没事，还在作战中！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.50,0:18:36.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.87,0:18:41.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是没用！\N还在这样子...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:42.04,0:18:46.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连雪拉和凯也及不上...\N可恶...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.18,0:18:48.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你怎可以这样说，隼人！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:49.15,0:18:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不是已经很英勇吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你不用来安慰我了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.49,0:18:56.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不怕老实对你说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:57.02,0:18:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,自从我上了母舰后\N到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.49,0:19:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,一直都还想赢阿姆罗的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:01.66,0:19:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但结果...\N始终无法胜过他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.66,0:19:08.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,隼人，阿姆罗他...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.27,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是和我们不同的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:10.50,0:19:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我们不同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:22.45,0:19:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第二和第六战斗队\N已没回音！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.02,0:19:26.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武断号亦失去联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.12,0:19:29.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,马加，给我一杯咖啡   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:29.79,0:19:31.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,吩咐所有MS出去防守
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要将敌人全部消灭！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.81,0:19:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他们想撤退？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.38,0:19:51.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从那里冲入去较好呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:54.48,0:19:56.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那里，是被新武器\N所毁坏的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.22,0:19:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,真利害！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.72,0:20:02.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,来吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.53,0:20:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,母舰有电讯！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.33,0:20:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,他说钢弹已攻入基地内了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.90,0:20:17.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好！吩咐\N各舰队MS出去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.84,0:20:20.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道！各舰队\N请听主舰命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:20.77,0:20:23.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派吉姆和铁球及\N各登陆部队出动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:36.69,0:20:38.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,希望大家\N可以顺利攻入去！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.28,0:21:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所罗门要求支援？   是！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.88,0:21:05.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由暗码打来的\N详情仍未清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:06.35,0:21:08.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是希莉亚将军吩咐的命令
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.89,0:21:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,要求我们出战\N支援所罗门！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.16,0:21:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,拉拉，怎样？\N我们要进入战场了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.67,0:21:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,赞斯巴尔，全速前进！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.97,0:21:23.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,目的地，所罗门！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.84,0:21:25.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,各人回去作战岗位！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:42.89,0:21:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还生存吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.70,0:21:53.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,米莱，加油啊！\N你要继续努力啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:55.00,0:21:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,邵娜在吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:57.80,0:21:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,亲爱的\N这里是不安全吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:00.21,0:22:02.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别胡说\N所罗门不会沦陷的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:02.81,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是...         听我说！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.61,0:22:06.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想你去姊姊的\N格拉纳达处避避
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:06.81,0:22:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这里怎办？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.21,0:22:09.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,别担心，这里没事的！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:11.65,0:22:14.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宝贝交给你了！\N你要养育她成人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:14.35,0:22:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道吗？邵娜！      你...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.69,0:22:19.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,因为我是一个军人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:20.13,0:22:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,所以要维护\N我们萨比家军人的尊严
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:24.30,0:22:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我不会死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.77,0:22:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,快点，带同宝宝\N一起走，邵娜！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:39.65,0:22:41.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,编成MS作战队伍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:41.45,0:22:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,敌人快登陆了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:43.18,0:22:45.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,萨克，多姆准备出发
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.02,0:22:49.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,武装火箭炮部队\N全出战对付敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:50.32,0:22:51.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,毕克．萨姆准备妥当没有？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:51.62,0:22:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在准备要大进攻了！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.90,0:23:00.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个...就是毕克．萨姆！

